Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:21.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,200)}俯き過ぎて小さい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:26.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(0,200)}僕だけの景色が
